name: Brussels ThinkLab
goal: Brussels ThinkLab is a centre of excellence that aims to promote best practice in regional development, and to help regional governments to develop projects for the economic development of their communities.
interests: Agriculture and Rural Development, Culture, Culture and media, Digital economy and society, Employment and Social Affairs, Energy, Environment, Regional Policy, Transport
euInitiatives: Regional development, rural development, structural funds, environmental policy, energy, transport, employment and social affairs.
